## 关键命令

所有命令在项目根目录执行。

### 开发环境初始化
```bash
# 【TODO: 克隆后首次设置】
git clone 【TODO: repo-url】
# Unity: 用 Unity Hub 打开项目，等待依赖解析完成
# Unreal: 右键 .uproject → Generate Visual Studio project files → 编译
# C++: cmake -B build -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug && cmake --build build
```

### 构建
```bash
# 【TODO: 选择并修改】
# Unity CLI Build:
#   unity -quit -batchmode -projectPath . -executeMethod BuildScript.Build -logFile build.log

# Unreal Build:
#   RunUAT BuildCookRun -project=YourProject.uproject -platform=Win64 -configuration=Development

# C++ Server:
#   cmake --build build --config Release
```

### 运行测试
```bash
# Unity Test Runner (EditMode):
#   unity -runTests -testPlatform EditMode -testResults results.xml

# Unreal Automation:
#   UnrealEditor-Cmd.exe YourProject -ExecCmds="Automation RunTests All"

# C++ (GoogleTest):
#   cd build && ctest --output-on-failure
```

### 部署
```bash
# 【TODO: iOS/Android/PC/Console 部署命令】
# iOS: archive + xcodebuild -exportArchive
# Android: gradlew assembleRelease → APK/AAB
# PC: 直接打包输出，或 CI 流程
# 服务器: docker build + docker push + k8s apply / ssh rsync
```

### 代码检查
```bash
# 【TODO: lint / format / static analysis】
